{"tid":2240033,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃之鋒：終於畢業啦！我選擇更為專注的投入公共事務，與大家一起留港作戰，Stay and Fight。","createTime":"2020-10-12T11:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T09:15:51.000Z","uid":271829,"like":94,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ea3c4060ed39a1c7be4602a2f673d24d52e2a762","tid":2240033,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/121258705_3417154698377014_266955470486842884_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=32sogm4E9LkAX9FBV3g&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg6-1.fna&amp;tp=7&amp;oh=24d7b73962a9c50f103ba0b92311f241&amp;oe=5FA8F78C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F121258705_3417154698377014_266955470486842884_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3D32sogm4E9LkAX9FBV3g%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg6-1.fna%26tp%3D7%26oh%3D24d7b73962a9c50f103ba0b92311f241%26oe%3D5FA8F78C&h=56577fb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃之鋒：<br />\n【終於畢業啦！】<br />\n今天，我收到公開大學學分承認及畢業組來信，校方確認我已完成社會科學學士（政治及公共行政）的課程，大學教務會亦核准我以Second Class Honours （Upper Divison）畢業。<br />\n從2014年入學至今，可說是歷盡波折，我曾因判囚坐監而停學，亦試過在荔枝角收押所裡應考試，過去總笑說「雨傘幾多年我就讀咗幾多年」，如今終於順利畢業，總算完成一個心願。<br />\n六年以來，衷心感激教授過我的教授和老師多番照顧，以及曾在課堂擦身而過的同學抱有的體諒；即使大學本身立場保守，校長更被傳為地下共產黨員，但於我在學期間，校方從來沒向我施壓，也得來不易。<br />\n對很多同輩來說，大學畢業可能是步入人生下一階段的轉捩點，不過在我而言，說實話沒有非常強烈的感覺，反正個人也不太可以有人生規劃，畢竟前路已受官司訴訟和政治風暴所限。<br />\n有關個人去向，既然因遭限制離境而不可能遠赴海外深造，在港亦因不知何時面對監禁而難以進修，甚至擁有人身自由的時間說不定一直也在倒數，我選擇更為專注的投入公共事務，與大家一起留港作戰，Stay and Fight。<br />\n<br />\n更多：<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/42658863\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2F42658863&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=559bd401\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/42658863</a><br />\n<br />\n．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．<br />\n✍️聯署要求送返十二名被捕港人：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/save12youthspetitions\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fsave12youthspetitions&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=92dee4d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/save12youthspetitions</a><br />\n💪小額支持我的獨家分析及文章：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/joshuawonghk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fjoshuawonghk&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=44deb90b\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/joshuawonghk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/入學-6-年經歷入獄休學-黃之鋒順利從公開大學畢業-稱難得校方多年從未施壓/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%85%A5%E5%AD%B8-6-%E5%B9%B4%E7%B6%93%E6%AD%B7%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%84%E4%BC%91%E5%AD%B8-%E9%BB%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%8B%92%E9%A0%86%E5%88%A9%E5%BE%9E%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD-%E7%A8%B1%E9%9B%A3%E5%BE%97%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E5%A4%9A%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%9E%E6%9C%AA%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93%2F&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=4d918c07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%85%A5%E5%AD%B8-6-%E5%B9%B4%E7%B6%93%E6%AD%B7%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%84%E4%BC%91%E5%AD%B8-%E9%BB%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%8B%92%E9%A0%86%E5%88%A9%E5%BE%9E%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD-%E7%A8%B1%E9%9B%A3%E5%BE%97%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E5%A4%9A%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%9E%E6%9C%AA%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93%2F&h=e44d839c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/入學-6-年經歷入獄休學-黃之鋒順利從公開大學畢業-稱難得校方多年從未施壓/</a>"},{"pid":"05be89cf0ea149c38795abc09413b53dcf3464b6","tid":2240033,"uid":141837,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:28:37.000Z","msg":"一大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c877678d44d336722328527153e34cfcb1ad38","tid":2240033,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf96ae073e29f90fde7b0e037fdd2b3a39a9c02","tid":2240033,"uid"